quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  25,68,"Uye avo vasingadani vamwe vanamwari pamwechete naAllah, uye havauraye munhu uyo Allah wavakarambidza kusara pane chinangwa chakakodzera, uye havaite chehupombwe. Uye uyo anoita izvi achawana murango (unorwadza)"
  25,69,"Marwadzo achapamidzwa kaviri paari pazuva rekutongwa, uye achagaramo akadzikisirwa (achinyadziswa)"
  25,70,"Kusara kweuyo anokumbira ruregerero (anoita Taubah) uye otenda (muhumwechete hwaAllah), uye oita mabasa akanaka. Ava Allah vachachinja zvitadzo zvavo zvova mabasa akanaka, uye Allah vanoregerera zvikuru, uye vane tsitsi dzose"
  25,71,"Uye uyo anokumbira ruregerero uye oita mabasa akanaka, zvirokwazvo, anokumbira ruregerero rwaAllah nekumbiro yechokwadi"
  25,72,"Uye avo vasingapi uchapupu hwemanyepo, uye vakadarika nepari kutaurwa zvakashata kana pari kutambwa zvakashata, vanodarikapo vane rukudzo"
  25,73,"Uye avo vokuti kana vakarangaridzwa mashoko aTenzi vavo, havaite sekunge vasinganzwi (vanamatsi) kana mapofu kwaari"
  25,74,"Uye avo vanotaura kuti: “Tenzi vedu! Isai matiri runyevenuko rwemeso edu pavakadzi vedu uye vana vedu, uye tiitei vatungamiriri veavo vanotya Allah.”"
  25,75,Avo vachapiwa mugove wenzvimbo yepamusoro-soro muParadhiso nokuda kwekutsungirira kwavo. Varimo vachasanganikwa navo nekwaziso uye mashoko erugare uye rukudzo
  25,76,Vachagaramo (zvisingaperi). Inzvimbo yakanaka yokugara uye nzvimbo yokuzororera
  25,77,"Taura kuti (Muhammad (SAW) kune vasingatendi): “Tenzi wangu vanotarira kwamuri nokuda kwekuita kwenyu maDua (Minamato) kwavari. Asi zvino mavaramba. Saka murango uchava wenyu zvachose.”"